<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<img src="bi.gif" alt="The Beer Institute">
<center>
<ul>	<li><a href="/fun/cook.htm">Recipes</a>
	<li><a href="/bicaf/bicaf.htm">Corporate Philanthropy</a>
	<li><a href="/stats/econ.htm">Economic Contribution of the Beer Industry</a>
