<head>
<title>Brewers Almanac</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<h1>The Brewers Almanac</h1>
Jump to the <a href="#table">Sample Tables</a>
<h2>Brewers Almanac Table of Contents</h2>
<center>
<table>
<tr><td><ul>
<li>CHAPTER 1      APPRAISAL OF A MAJOR INDUSTRY
<li>CHAPTER 2      GAUGING THE INDUSTRY'S SCOPE 
