<center>
<ul>	<li><a href="./fun/cook.htm">Recipes</a>	<li><a href="./bicaf/bicaf.htm">Beer Institute Community Assistance Fund</a>	<li><a href="./stats/econ.htm">Economic Contribution of the Beer Industry</a>	<li><a href="./action/edu.htm">Community Education Programs</a>	<li><a href="./environ/environ.htm">Environmental Commitment</a>	<li><a href="./pubs/pubs.htm">Publications</a>	<li><a href="./beerinst/inst.htm">The Beer Institute</a>
