<h2>How Different Industries Share the Economic Contribution of the Beer Industry in the
United States</h2>

<i>Excerpted From <A Href="../pubs/pubs.htm#econ">Brewing: A Story of Economic Impact</a>
compiled by Steve L. Barsby & Associates, Inc.
