<DOCHDR>
http://beerinst.org:80/inst/papers/bottle.htm 204.91.135.4 19970107133616 text/html 4898
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Enterprise/2.0a
Date: Mon, 06 Jan 1997 21:41:05 GMT
Accept-ranges: bytes
Last-modified: Thu, 04 Apr 1996 16:52:10 GMT
Content-length: 4693
