<H1><A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="images/tualogo1.gif" ALIGN=TOP BORDER=0 ALT="TUANZ"></A> About the creators</H1>

<PRE>

</PRE>

<BLOCKQUOTE>

<H3><A HREF="mailto:miskelly@actrix.gen.nz">Adrian Miskelly</A></H3>

<P>
 Adrian Miskelly has just completed his degree in Visual Communication
 Design at Wellington Polytechnic. His speciality is Interface Design for
 multimedia and the World Wide Web.
</P>
<P>
 Adrian is 24 years old and would ultimately like to design the
 international standard interface for Virtual Reality. He is a freelance
 designer and sub contracts as a graphic artist to Corporate Publishers in
 Wellington.
</P>

<PRE>

</PRE>

<H3><A HREF="mailto:kennett@actrix.gen.nz">Paul Kennett</A></H3>

<P>
 Paul Kennett works as HTML/Web builder for Kennett Brothers Web Design.
 Recent projects include; <A HREF="http://www.wcc.govt.nz">Wellington.net</A>,
 <A HREF="http://www.actrix.gen.nz">Actrix</A>,
 <A HREF="http://www.actrix.gen.nz/govt/tpk">Te Puki Korkiri Ministry of Maori Development</A>,
 <A HREF="http://www.moca.govt.nz">Ministry of Cultural Affairs</A>,
 <A HREF="http://www.actrix.gen.nz/biz/chenpalm">Chen &amp; Palmer</A> and the 
 <A HREF="http://www.mountainbike.co.nz">New Zealand Mountain Bike Web</A>.
</P>
<P>
 Paul is 31 years old and lives in Wellington. He has previously worked as a computer technician,
 network/systems manager, publisher, graphic designer, author, reporter, editor,
 sports event manager, bicycle mechanic and professional mountain bike racer.
</P>

</BLOCKQUOTE>


