<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="#contents"><IMG SRC="images/header.gif" WIDTH=400 HEIGHT=88 BORDER=0 alt="The Maori Law Review"></A></H1>
<P>
<BR>
<BR>
</P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
 The Maori Law Review is a reporter of law affecting Maori, the
 indigenous people of New Zealand/Aotearoa. The Review covers decisions of the Maori
 Land Court and general courts, reports of the Waitangi Tribunal and publications
 of government and law schools.
<P>

 This site complements the printed version and contains 
 the full text of all issues except the latest two months.
<A NAME="contents"> </a>
<BR>

