	<HEAD>
		<TITLE>The Clarke Institute: Thanks to Our Partners</TITLE>
		<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:dave@thom.com">
	</HEAD>

	<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#CC6600" ALINK="#FFFFFF" VLINK="#000000">
		<TABLE WIDTH=600 BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0><TR VALIGN=TOP><TD COLSPAN=3>
			<H1><IMG ALT="Thanks to Our Partners" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=169
					 SRC="images/thanks_to_partners_h.gif"></H1></TR>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=170 HEIGHT=1>

		<TD><IMG ALT="" WIDTH=350 HEIGHT=1 SRC="images/spacer.gif">
			<P>In mid-1995, a small group of forward thinking people at
			The Clarke foresaw the tremendous potential of the emerging
			new media to contribute to patient care, education and
			research in mental health. After serious thought and
			discussion, our Senior Management Group and Board of
			Trustees committed to give this project their unqualified
			support.</P>
			
			<P>In these difficult economic times, however, it was a
			particularly challenging decision to invest in the
			development of innovative uses of internet technologies to
			distribute information and create dynamic new services for
			our patients, their caregivers and the wide range of
			professionals with whom we work.</P>
			
			<P>Fortunately, a group of dedicated volunteers and generous
			corporate patrons saw the tremendous value of our internet
			project and immediately leaped to the task of bringing it to
			life. </P>
			
			<P>We are deeply grateful to these people and organizations.
			Without their generous donations of time, money, and in-kind
			resources we simply wouldn't be here today.</P>
			
			<P>These individuals deserve particular recognition for
			their generous support and contributions:</P>
			
			<P><B>Individuals</B></P>
			
			<P><A HREF="mailto:gabriele@istar.ca">Sandra Gabriele</A><BR>
			<I>Gabriele Design</I></P>
			
			<P><A HREF="mailto:dave@thom.com">David Veldhuizen</A><BR>
			<I><A HREF="http://www.thom.com/">HTM Interactive Inc.</A></I></P>
			
			<P>Scott Nelson<BR>
			<I>Burning Chrome</I></P>
			
			<P>Don Tapscott<BR>
			<I>Author<BR>
			President, New Paradigm Learning Corporation</I></P>
			
			<P><A HREF="mailto:comstrat@inforamp.net">Tony Long</A><BR>
			<I><A HREF="http://www.inforamp.net/~comstrat/">The Long Group version 2.0 Inc.</A></I></P>
			
			<P>Jim Warrillow<BR>
			<I>MacLean Hunter Publications</I></P>
			
			<P>Jim Hall<BR>
			<I>Maclean Hunter Medical Publications &amp; Communication</I></P>
			
			<P>Janet E. Yorston, M.D. CCFP.<BR>
			<I>University of Toronto<BR>
			Victoria Health Centre</I></P>
			
			<P><B>Corporations</B></P>
			
			<P>Maclean Hunter Medical Publications &amp; Communications</P>
			
			<P><A HREF="http://www.sun.com/"><IMG ALT="Sun Microsystems"
				WIDTH=83 HEIGHT=36 SRC="images/sun.gif" BORDER=0></A></P>
			
			<P><A HREF="http://www.inforamp.net/~comstrat/">The Long Group version 2.0 Inc.</A></P>
			
			<P><A HREF="mailto:gabriele@istar.ca">Gabriele Design</A></P>
			
			<P><A HREF="http://www.thom.com/"><IMG ALT="HTM Interactive Inc."
				WIDTH=91 HEIGHT=59 SRC="images/htm_interactive.gif" BORDER=0></A></P>

