			<TD>Please enter a word or word fragment to search for:
			<FORM METHOD=POST ACTION="search.cgi">
				<P><INPUT NAME="query_string" SIZE=40></INPUT>
				<IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=1>
				<INPUT TYPE="submit" VALUE="Search"></P>
			</FORM>
			
			<HR>
			
			<P>Here are some hints to help make your search more
			effective:</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG SRC="images/bullet.gif"
				ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=5 HEIGHT=5 VSPACE=2 HSPACE=2 ALT="*">
			<TD><P>Word fragments are matched. For example, &quot;schizophreni&quot;
			matches both &quot;schizophrenia&quot; and &quot;schizophrenic&quot;.</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG SRC="images/bullet.gif"
				ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=5 HEIGHT=5 VSPACE=2 HSPACE=2 ALT="*">
			<TD><P>Searches are not case-sensitive.</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG SRC="images/bullet.gif"
				ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=5 HEIGHT=5 VSPACE=2 HSPACE=2 ALT="*">
			<TD><P>If you search for a phrase and do not get any matches,
			try searching for a single word or word fragment.</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG SRC="images/bullet.gif"
				ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=5 HEIGHT=5 VSPACE=2 HSPACE=2 ALT="*">
			<TD><P>Do not use wildcards or regular expressions.</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD COLSPAN=3><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=30>
