	<HEAD>
		<TITLE>The Clarke Institute: Current Events: Music For Midwinter</TITLE>
		<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:dave@thom.com">
	</HEAD>

	<BODY BACKGROUND="../images/musical_gift_logo.gif" TEXT="#000000"
		  LINK="#FF9900" ALINK="#FFFFFF" VLINK="#000000">
		<TABLE WIDTH=600 BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0><TR VALIGN=TOP><TD COLSPAN=3>
			<H1><IMG ALT="Current Events" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=169
					 SRC="../images/current_events_h.gif"></H1></TR>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=170 HEIGHT=20>
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=345 HEIGHT=20>			
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD>
			<TD><P><B><IMG ALT="Music For Midwinter"
			SRC="../images/music_for_midwinter.gif" WIDTH=302 HEIGHT=26></B></P>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD>
			<TD><P>On eight consecutive Tuesday nights in January and
			February 1997, leading Canadian Musicians will be
			contributing their time and talent to stage a series of
			concerts at The Clarke. The series has been organized by
			curator Mary Lou Fallis and patron Diana Tremain to provide
			a welcome hour of entertainment and relaxation for Clarke
			clients, families, volunteers, staff and community. The
			concert series has been made possible thanks to a generous
			donation specifically for this series. Each performance will
			run from 5:30 to 6:30 pm in the Auditorium of The Clarke;
			admission is free.</P>
			
			<P>January 7 -- <B>Prima donna on a Moose</B> -- Singer Mary
			Lou Fallis</P>
			
			<P>January 14 -- <B>Dr. Music at The Clarke</B> -- Jazzman
			Doug Riley</P>
			
			<P>January 21 -- <B>All the Basses Covered</B> -- Double
			Bass Quartet from Toronto Symphony</P>
			
			<P>January 28 -- <B>Lucky Seven</B> -- Seven classical
			musicians from major Toronto shows</P>
			
			<P>February 4 -- <B>Clarke at The Clarke</B> -- featuring 3
			internationally-known chamber musicians</P>
			
			<P>February 11 -- <B>If It's Tuesday, It Must Be Tabla</B>
			-- with Ritesh Das &amp; the Toronto Tabla Ensemble</P>
			
			<P>February 18 -- <B>A Latin Valentine</B> -- Edgardo Moreno
			&amp; Friends</P>
			
			<P>February 25 -- <B>Country Finale</B> -- Caitlin Hanford
			&amp; Chris Whiteley</P>


		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD COLSPAN=3><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=30>
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD><P ALIGN=RIGHT>
				<A HREF="../contents.html"><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/back_button_wt.gif"
					WIDTH=154 HEIGHT=58 BORDER=0 HSPACE=8></A></P>
			<TD><P><I><A HREF="../contents.html">Back to Main Contents</A></I></P>
