			much assistance as possible to the many journalists who
			contact The Clarke. We hope that many of your questions will
			be answered here.</I></P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_bk.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE=8>
