			HREF="release_archive.html">an archive</A> of older releases.</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_bk.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE=8>
			<TD><P><A HREF="mailto:comstrat@inforamp.net">E-mail Your Questions</A></P>
			
			<P>If you need information, but you don't necessarily need
			an in-person interview, send us your questions by email. Be
			sure to give us your phone number! Our Communication
			Department will either get you the information or arrange to
			have one of our specialist professionals get back to you
			promptly. We'll get back to you as quickly as we can... at
			the very least within 24 hours.</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_bk.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE=8>
			<TD><P>If you need to talk to a real live person...</P>
			
			<P>Of course, you are always welcome to call whomever you
			like at The Clarke. Our <A HREF="../about_the_clarke/contacting_staff.html">phone
			directory</A> will help. Our professional staff, however,
			spend virtually all of their time in patient care, research
			and education so your call probably won't get the quick
			priority that you need.</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_bk.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE=8>
			<TD><P>Communication Department</P>
			
			<P>We recommend that you first call one of the staff in our
			Communication Department. It's their job to quickly get you
			the facts or the interview you need. Please call Ms.
			Jean-Ann Lowry at (416) 979-2734</P>

