	<HEAD>
		<TITLE>The Clarke Institute: Links To Independent Support Sites</TITLE>
		<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:dave@thom.com">
	</HEAD>

	<BODY BGCOLOR="#FF9900" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#003333" ALINK="#FF9900" VLINK="#000000">
		<TABLE WIDTH=600 BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0>
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD COLSPAN=3>
			<H1><IMG ALT="Links To Independent Support Sites" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=169
					 SRC="images/links_h.gif"></H1>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=170 HEIGHT=20>
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=345 HEIGHT=20>			
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD>
			<TD><P>Welcome to The Clarke web library.</P>
			
			<P>This is the location for selected web resources in
			psychiatry, research, community support and other topics.
			The list is far from complete. In reviewing these selections
			please bear in mind that The Clarke cannot control the
			content or format of sites outside its own and cannot be
			held responsible for any advice or information they may
			offer. Our goal in maintaining this list is to offer another
			tool in the search for information and people with something
			positive to contribute on the subject of mental health.
			
			<P>We are always looking for other informative sites. If you
			know of a site that you think should be listed here, please
			<A HREF="mailto:comstrat@inforamp.net">tell us</A> where it
			is and why you recommend it.</P>
			
			<P>Thank you.</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=170 HEIGHT=20>
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=345 HEIGHT=20>			
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>

