			<A HREF="http://www.social.com/health/nhic/data/hr2200/hr2296.html">http://www.social.com/health/nhic/data/hr2200/hr2296.html</A></P>
			
			<P>National Institute on Drug Abuse:<BR>
			<A HREF="http://www.nida.nih.gov/">http://www.nida.nih.gov/</A></P>
		
			<P>Royal Ottawa Health Care Group:<BR>
			<A HREF="http://www.rohcg.on.ca/index.html">http://www.rohcg.on.ca/index.html</A></P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=170 HEIGHT=20>
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=345 HEIGHT=20>			
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD>
			<TD><P><IMG ALT="University Psychiatric Departments"
						SRC="images/links_university.gif" WIDTH=289 HEIGHT=26 BORDER=0></P>
		
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD>
			<TD><P>NYU Department of Psychiatry:<BR>
			<A HREF="http://www.med.nyu.edu/Psych/">http://www.med.nyu.edu/Psych/</A></P>
			
			<P>Western Psychiatric Institute and Clinic, Department of Psychiatry, Univ. of Pittsburgh:<BR>
			<A HREF="http://www.wpic.pitt.edu/">http://www.wpic.pitt.edu/</A></P>
			
			<P>Yale Department of Psychiatry:<BR>
			<A HREF="http://info.med.yale.edu/psych">http://info.med.yale.edu/psych</A></P>
		
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=170 HEIGHT=20>
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=345 HEIGHT=20>			
