	<HEAD>
		<TITLE>The Clarke Institute: About The Clarke: Welcome by Dr. Garfinkel</TITLE>
		<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:dave@thom.com">
	</HEAD>

	<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#CC6600" ALINK="#FFFFFF" VLINK="#000000">
		<TABLE WIDTH=600 BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0>
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD COLSPAN=4>
			<H1><IMG ALT="Welcome by Dr. Garfinkel" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=169
					 SRC="../images/garfinkel_h.gif"></H1></TR>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=20>
					 <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=20>			
					 <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=350 HEIGHT=20>			
					 <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
		<TD ROWSPAN=4><IMG ALT="Photo: Dr. Garfinkel" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=150 SRC="../images/garfinkel_photo.gif">

		<TD><TD><P>Welcome to The Clarke Institute of Psychiatry website!
		We've built this site to:</P>
		
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG SRC="../images/bullet.gif"
				ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=5 HEIGHT=5 VSPACE=2 HSPACE=2 ALT="*">
			<TD><P>Tell visitors about our services and activities;</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG SRC="../images/bullet.gif"
				ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=5 HEIGHT=5 VSPACE=2 HSPACE=2 ALT="*">
			<TD><P>Stimulate the flow of ideas and solutions among
			mental health professionals, and</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG SRC="../images/bullet.gif"
				ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=5 HEIGHT=5 VSPACE=2 HSPACE=2 ALT="*">
			<TD><P>Initiate dynamic new services for our patients, their
			caregivers, and the many professionals with whom we work.</P>
			
			<P>Please explore our site and give us feedback about your
			experience.</P>
			
			<P>Established 30 years ago, The Clarke Institute of
			Psychiatry (The Clarke) conducts research into psychiatric
			illness, trains mental health professionals, and cares for
			people suffering from mental health problems. From the
			beginning we have enjoyed a unique academic relationship
			with the Department of Psychiatry at the University of
			Toronto and have fulfilled both a provincial and local role
			in providing care and training. Over the years, tens of
			thousands of patients and their families have received
			excellent care, while several generations of mental health
			professionals have been trained at The Clarke. This year we
			will provide assessment and treatment to more people than
			ever before and will participate in the training of over 330
			students in the mental health disciplines.</P>
			
			<P>As for research, the contributions of The Clarke
			researchers to our understanding and treatment of
			psychiatric disorders has been recognized around the world.
			Over the past five years the amount of research money
			awarded to The Clarke researchers has quadrupled -- a
			remarkable accomplishment at a time of intense competition
			for shrinking research dollars. This funding will enable The
			Clarke to continue to play a key role in understanding how
			mental illnesses develop and how to treat them cost
			effectively.</P>
			
			<P>The Clarke Institute of Psychiatry is a unique
			organization with a distinguished history. We intend to
			maintain our high standards of care, research and education,
			and to work with others. Our goals are to lead in the battle
			against mental illness, and to improve the quality of life
			of those we treat and serve.</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
		<TD COLSPAN=2><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=165 HEIGHT=40>
			<IMG ALT="U. of T. Logo" WIDTH=67 HEIGHT=86 ALIGN=RIGHT
				 HSPACE=10 SRC="../images/garfinkel_uoft.gif">

		<TD><P>Paul E. Garfinkel, M.D.., F.R.C.P. (C),</P>

			<P><I>President and CEO and Psychiatrist in Chief<BR>
			Clarke Institute of Psychiatry</I></P>
			
			<P><I>Professor and Chair,<BR>
			Department of Psychiatry<BR>
			University of Toronto</I></P>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD COLSPAN=4><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=30>
