	<HEAD>
		<TITLE>The Clarke Institute: About The Clarke: Annual Report</TITLE>
		<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:dave@thom.com">
	</HEAD>

	<BODY BACKGROUND="../images/30_year_logo.gif" TEXT="#000000"
		  LINK="#CC6600" ALINK="#FFFFFF" VLINK="#000000">
		<TABLE WIDTH=600 BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0><TR VALIGN=TOP><TD COLSPAN=3>
			<H1><IMG ALT="1995-96 Annual Report" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=169
					 SRC="../images/annual_report_h.gif"></H1></TR>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=170 HEIGHT=20>
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=345 HEIGHT=20>			
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD>
			<TD><P><I>This is an abridged version of the Annual Report for
			our 1995-96 fiscal year. The complete document is available
			as an Acrobat file.</I> [<A HREF="annual_report.pdf">PDF,
			1.2Mb</A>]</P>
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_wt_sm.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=6 HEIGHT=6 HSPACE=8 VSPACE=3>
			<TD><A HREF="#Mission_Statement">Mission Statement</A>
			<TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>
		
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_wt_sm.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=6 HEIGHT=6 HSPACE=8 VSPACE=3>
			<TD><A HREF="#Our_Leadership">Our Leadership</A>
			<TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>
		
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_wt_sm.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=6 HEIGHT=6 HSPACE=8 VSPACE=3>
			<TD><A HREF="#Battle">Leadership in The Battle Against Mental Illness</A>
			<TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>
		
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_wt_sm.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=6 HEIGHT=6 HSPACE=8 VSPACE=3>
			<TD><A HREF="#30_Years_On">30 Years On: An Overview</A>
			<TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>
		
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_wt_sm.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=6 HEIGHT=6 HSPACE=8 VSPACE=3>
			<TD><A HREF="#Financial_Statements">Financial Statements</A>
			<TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=40>
		
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD>
			<TD><P><B><A NAME="Mission_Statement"><IMG ALT="Mission Statement"
				SRC="../images/annual_report_mission.gif" WIDTH=302 HEIGHT=26></A></B></P>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD><IMG ALT="[Photo]" SRC="../images/annual_report_building.gif" WIDTH=147 HEIGHT=208>
			<TD><P><B>Our Vision</B></P>
				
				<P>To provide leadership in the battle against mental
				illness.</P>
				
				<B>Our Mission</B>
				
				<P>To improve the quality of life for people affected by
				mental illness through innovative research, effective
				clinical care, and dissemination of knowledge.</P>
				
				<B>Our Philosophy</B>
				
				<P>We are a psychiatric research institute and teaching
				hospital devoted to serving people with mental health
				problems in Ontario. We combine research, education and
				clinical care, and focus on areas of highest need where we
				have established expertise.</P>
				
				<B>Research</B>
				
				<P>Striving for the highest standards of excellence and
				ethics in our research. Integrating research across the
				spectrum from the 'laboratory to the community.'</P>
				
				<B>Education</B>
				
				<P>Improving the standard of mental health practice across
				Ontario through professional education. Transferring
				knowledge from research to practice through consultation,
				technical support and policy research. Providing accessible
				public education to increase understanding, reduce stigma,
				and advocate against contributors to mental illness.</P>
				
				<B>Clinical Care</B>
				
				<P>Caring for patients in the most compassionate manner and
				least intrusive setting, with input from patients/clients
				and families, and employing multidisciplinary teams.</P>
				
				<P>Exemplifying the best current practice in our
				development, use and teaching of clinical programs.
				Collaborating with appropriate sectors of the mental health
				care system to deliver comprehensive and cost-effective
				service.</P>
				
				<B>Operating Principles</B>
				
				<P>We are accountable to individuals and organizations in
				the community -- our external stakeholders. We acknowledge
				this responsibility through continuous evaluation of the
				effectiveness and efficiency of our services in all areas.
				We believe cooperation, fairness and respect for individual
				dignity is paramount in relations with patients/clients,
				families, staff, volunteers and community. We are committed
				to providing an environment that supports professional and
				personal development of all our staff and optimal health and
				safety in the workplace.</P><BR>


			<P><B><A NAME="Our_Leadership"><IMG ALT="Our Leadership"
			SRC="../images/annual_report_leadership.gif" WIDTH=302 HEIGHT=26></A></B></P>
				
				<P><B>Board of Trustees</B></P>
