<DOCHDR>
http://cip.clarke-inst.on.ca:80/media_information/96-07-02.html 192.197.205.222 19970121055957 text/html 8186
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 05:56:28 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 17-Dec-96 21:02:41 GMT
Content-length: 7995
Content-type: text/html
