	<HEAD>
		<TITLE>The Clarke Institute: About The Clarke: How to Travel to The Clarke</TITLE>
		<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:dave@thom.com">
	</HEAD>

	<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#CC6600" ALINK="#FFFFFF" VLINK="#000000">
		<TABLE WIDTH=600 BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0>
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD COLSPAN=3>
			<H1><IMG ALT="How to Travel to The Clarke" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=169
					 SRC="../images/travel_h.gif"></H1>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=170 HEIGHT=20>
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=345 HEIGHT=20>			
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=20>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD>
			<TD><P>The Clarke Institute of Psychiatry is located in the
			heart of downtown Toronto, Ontario at 250 College Street,
			just a little east of Spadina Avenue. If you are coming by
			public transit (the easiest way) the TTC's Spadina #77 bus
			or the Carlton #506 Streetcar both stop only steps away from
			our front door. If you're coming by car, be aware that
			parking is very limited. There is a parking garage we share
			with the <A HREF="http://www.arf.org/">Addiction Research
			Foundation</A>; the entrance is off Spadina just north of
			College. The garage is often full during the day, but you
			can usually find a spot in the evening. There is some
			metered parking on Spadina and there is the Kensington
			Municipal Parking lot south off Spadina. If you're coming by
			bike, there are bike racks by the Spadina entrance.</P>
			
			<P>There are 2 entrances, the main entrance on College
			Street and the Spadina entrance at the bottom of the
			driveway off Spadina, just north of College (best spot for
			drop-off.)</P>
			
			<P>Here's a <A HREF="map.html">map of the area</A>.
			
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD COLSPAN=3><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=30>
		<TR VALIGN=TOP>
			<TD><P ALIGN=RIGHT>
				<A HREF="../contents.html"><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/back_button_wt.gif"
					WIDTH=154 HEIGHT=58 BORDER=0 HSPACE=8></A></P>
			<TD><P><I><A HREF="../contents.html">Back to Main Contents</A></I></P>
		</TABLE>
	</BODY>
