<DOCHDR>
http://cip.clarke-inst.on.ca:80/about_services/research_division.html 192.197.205.222 19970121060718 text/html 6816
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 06:03:21 GMT
