	<HEAD>
		<TITLE>The Clarke Institute: About The Clarke: Structure and Organization</TITLE>
		<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:dave@thom.com">
	</HEAD>

	<BODY BGCOLOR="#003333" TEXT="#FFFFFF" LINK="#FF9900" ALINK="#003333" VLINK="#FFFFFF">
		<TABLE WIDTH=600 BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0>
		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD COLSPAN=3>
			<H1><IMG ALT="Structure and Organization" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=169
					 SRC="../images/structure_h.gif"></H1>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=170 HEIGHT=1>
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=345 HEIGHT=1>			
					   <TD><IMG ALT="" SRC="../images/spacer.gif" WIDTH=85 HEIGHT=1>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD>
			<TD><P>The Clarke Institute of Psychiatry is organized into
			seven clinical divisions and a research division. The
			clinical divisions are described briefly in this section.
			All our clinical services, clinical research and training of
			mental health professionals are carried out in these
			divisions. The Research Division is comprised of numerous
			research sections, reflecting both basic neuroscience and
			psychosocial approaches to understanding and treating mental
			illnesses.</P>
			
			<P>A relatively unique aspect of The Clarke's organization
			is that professional departments of child care work,
			nursing, occupational therapy, pharmacy, psychiatry,
			psychology, social work and speech therapy are maintained
			across the clinical divisions. This results in &quot;matrix
			organizational structure&quot; that allows us to deliver the
			best clinical care in the context of research and
			training.</P>

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_bk.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE=8>
			<TD><P><A HREF="child_care_work.html">Child Care Work Department</A></P>			

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_bk.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE=8>
			<TD><P><A HREF="family_court.html">Family Court Clinic</A></P>			

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_bk.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE=8>
			<TD><P><A HREF="forensic_division.html">Forensic Division</A></P>			

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_bk.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE=8>
			<TD><P><A HREF="general_psychiatry.html">General Psychiatry Division</A></P>			

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_bk.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE=8>
			<TD><P><A HREF="mood_and_anxiety.html">Mood and Anxiety Division</A></P>			

		<TR VALIGN=TOP><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><IMG ALT="*" SRC="../images/bullet_bk.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE=8>
